These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  freelancer, bartender, chef, dancer, doctor, nurse, journalist
There are 7 different nationalities: italian, indian, american, pakistani, indonesian, colombian, british
 1. the dancer is on the left of the pakistani##1
 2. the indonesian is the dancer##1
 3. the journalist is on the right of the nurse##1
 4. the american is on the right of the colombian##1
 5. the chef is in the middle##1
 6. the italian is on the far left##1
 7. the doctor is the italian##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the colombian##1
 9. the american is on the left of the indian##1
10. the pakistani is on the left of the chef##1
11. the journalist is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | doctor | dancer | bartender | chef | freelancer | nurse | journalist |
| Nationality   | italian    | indonesian   | pakistani      | colombian | american    | indian    | british         |

