.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: zucchini, papaya, pomegranate, tomato, kale, spinach, onion
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: dubstep, salsa, house, disco, folk, electronic, trance
 1. the fan of folk is the person eating tomato##1
 2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the fan of trance##1
 3. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating papaya is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the person eating tomato is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 7. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of folk is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 9. the fan of trance is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | zucchini | papaya | kale | tomato | spinach | onion | pomegranate |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | house   | disco   | folk      | dubstep       | trance       | electronic     |

