.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: radish, nectarine, garlic, papaya, asparagus, eggplant, strawberry
The people have 7 different jobs:  librarian, project-manager, videographer, designer, lawyer, journalist, nurse
 1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 2. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the nurse##1
 3. the project-manager is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 4. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
 5. the librarian is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the videographer is on the right of the project-manager##1
 7. the project-manager is on the left of the videographer##1
 8. the project-manager is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person eating eggplant is the designer##1
10. the person eating garlic is on the right of the librarian##1
11. the designer is in the middle##1
12. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | nectarine | asparagus     | garlic  | eggplant       | radish       | strawberry  | papaya   |
| Job    | journalist  | librarian | nurse | designer | project-manager | videographer | lawyer |

