.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, ambient, pop, hip-hop, trance, gospel, reggae
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, pakistani, mexican, russian, malaysian, canadian, polish
 1. the fan of trance is the pakistani##1
 2. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 3. the canadian is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the turkish is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 5. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 6. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
 7. the mexican is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 8. the fan of pop is on the right of the canadian##1
 9. the fan of pop is the malaysian##1
10. the malaysian is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
11. the polish is the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | reggae     | hip-hop     | pop      | ambient | trance      | classical     |
| Nationality   | russian | mexican | canadian | malaysian | polish | pakistani | turkish |

