.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, reading, collecting, woodworking, skydiving, dancing
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat, goat, pony, turtle, bird, hedgehog
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | hiking | reading | skydiving     | collecting | dancing | woodworking | filmmaking |
| Pet     | hedgehog   | goat    | turtle | bird     | chinchilla         | pony     | rat        |

