.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, fanta, cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, lemonade
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat, bike, motorbike, subway, car, taxi
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person drinking tea is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | fanta | mirinda   | tea | cola | lemonade  | hot-chocolate | milk |
| Transport   | motorbike   | subway | snowmobile | car     | boat | taxi | bike   |

