.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: horror, superhero, comedy, disaster, sports, spy, documentary
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, airplane, quad-bike, taxi, bus, ship, helicopter
 1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is the person driving the taxi##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is the person watching comedy movies##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | documentary | disaster | sports | spy     | superhero | comedy |
| Transport     | ship | taxi      | helicopter | quad-bike    | bus | airplane   | scooter  |

